meta.title: What Happened to OfficerPoop and Zak Wolf

ttsdata.text: Hey guys, it's me. Sean, otherwise known as Everything PC Gaming. I got a question for you guys? Whatever happened to Officer Poop? The younger goanimater whos character was a cop?
I was just wondering because he was the very first goanimator I ever watched apart from that one goanimate video talking critical of Littons Weekend Adventure from 2011.
First time I watched Officer Poops one video was in November 2014 and it's where KAI U poops on his dad very similar to this.
Poopy poopy everywhere. Poopy poopy in my underwear. Poopy poopy here it comes.
Oh oh oh oh oh oh! KAI U, how dare you poop on me. That's it. you are grounded grounded grounded for 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 years. Go to your room right now.
Like seriously, even though this particular short wasn't that great. It just got better from there with multiple goanimaters poping up. But his always struck me as the most edgy.
He's the goanimator which basically made boris's character into a sociopathic weapon wielding maniac
Another goanimator I have love and respect for is Zak Wolf. His video on KAI U and his mommy getting revenge on Boris I always found original and cutting edge for the time.
I seriously think you should subscribe to Zak Wolf as well as myself just because Zak's the guy who pretty much added to the popularity of goanimate as a whole.
